\u2019i on Criticism: Delivering criticism in the best way, without hyperbole","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, heard me one day as I said, \u201cThis narrator is a great liar!\u201d Al-Shafi\u2019i said to me, \u201cO Abu Ibrahim, dress your words in the best manner. Do not say this narrator is a great liar, but rather say his narrations\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26012,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/04\/only-knowledge-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":39046,"position":1},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: It is only knowledge if it benefits you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 4, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Rabia\u2019 reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cKnowledge is not merely what is memorized. Knowledge is what benefits.\u201d Source: al-Madkhal ila\u0301 al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 400 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0639 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0627\u0641\u0639\u064a \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u062d\u064f\u0641\u0650\u0638\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u0650\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0639\u064e 400 \u00a0\u0627\u0644\u0645\u062f\u062e\u0644 \u0625\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0628\u0631\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0647\u0642\u064a","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/shafiee-advice-private\/","url_meta":{"origin":39046,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Nasihah: Sincere advice is given in private, not public","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever admonishes his brother in private has been sincere to him and protected his reputation. Whoever admonishes him in public has humiliated him and betrayed him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 9\/140 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0632\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0638\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26826,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/10\/14\/shafii-arguing-deen-hate\/","url_meta":{"origin":39046,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debates: Arguing in religion breeds hate, bad will","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Rabia\u2019 ibn Sulayman reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cArguing about the religion hardens the heart and produces resentment.\u201d And Al-Shafi'i said, \"I never debated anyone but with sincere good will.\" Source: Siyar A'la\u0304m al-Nubala\u0304' 10\/28 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0639 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064f \u0641\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u0651\u0650\u064a\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34348,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/08\/04\/shafii-on-too-much-debate\/","url_meta":{"origin":39046,"position":4},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Debate: Too much debating belittles status of knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 4, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn \u2018Abd al-Hakam reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cAmong the degradation of knowledge is that you debate everyone who debates you, or you argue with everyone who argues with you.\u201d And he said, \u201cKnowledge is ignorance to the people of ignorance, just as ignorance is ignorance\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33953,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/27\/shafii-malice-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":39046,"position":5},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Malice: Forgiveness relieved my soul of anxiety","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, wrote in his poetry, \u201cWhen I forgave and stopped holding malice against anyone, I relieved my soul of the worries of enmity.\u201d Source: Di\u0304wa\u0304n al-Sha\u0304fi\u02bbi\u0304 31 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0627\u0641\u0639\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0641\u064a \u0634\u0639\u0631\u0647 \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0639\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u0652 \u0623\u062d\u0652\u0642\u0650\u062f\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u062d\u064e\u062f\u064d \u0623\u0631\u062d\u062a\u064f \u0646\u0641\u0633\u064a \u0645\u0646 \u0647\u0645\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u062f\u0627\u0648\u0627\u062a\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/39046","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=39046"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abu